{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act44side", "eventName": "墟", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AT-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "漩渦", "storyInfo": "在寄身金石電視台，卻對三船的所作所為深惡痛絕的更紗的幫助下，萌萌香和吉星與星熊取得了聯絡。而森內也了結了他多年來尋找某位神明的心願，儘管了結心願的方式出乎他的意料。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_towerinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#8$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊！星熊！！能聽到我說話嗎？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#8$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能聽到我——", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#8$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫什麼叫啊！", "name": "懈怠的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星——", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#14$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就叫吧，看看星熊那個傻瓜什麼時候來自投羅網！", "name": "懈怠的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……金兵衛到底想拿我怎麼樣？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金兵衛？那是誰？", "name": "懈怠的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我說三船。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#12$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼知道？不過，畢竟你多少也算個偶像，說不定會長拿你還有什麼別的用處，也說不定他就打算直接把你處理掉。", "name": "懈怠的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也真是的，白長了這麼一張漂亮的臉蛋，怎麼就不會向他低個頭呢？", "name": "懈怠的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*東國粗口*，明知道我被臨時拉來當看守，又是哪個混蛋傳訊息嘲笑我——", "name": "懈怠的黑道"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？又有一個倒楣鬼過來跟我換班？", "name": "懈怠的黑道"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀——哦！", "name": "懈怠的黑道"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……走遠了。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛到底是怎麼回事？為什麼能聽到其他人的聲音，甚至……好像還跟星熊說到話了？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道出現幻覺了？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在——你——的——背——後——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#10$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噗！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#10$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來你在節目裡的那些反應真的不是演的。之前吉星跟我說的時候我還不相信呢。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你認識吉星？吉星她怎麼樣了？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她和你差不多，也被關了起來。暫時應該不會吃什麼苦頭。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你到底是……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫我更紗吧，算是你的粉絲，名義上也算是三船的僱員。不過，我的真實身分其實是隱藏的忍客！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忍客？忍者？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要亂說，忍者只是拿錢辦事的殺人犯，我們忍客是城際網路的漫遊者好嗎！", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#4$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我記得忍客一開始不也是財閥養來攻擊競爭對手的忍者，只是精通城際網路的相關技術嗎？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，那就流浪忍客，流浪忍客好吧！", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#3$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是我還是不知道你從哪來的，也不知道你為什麼會幫我——", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在家看到的那段錄影，就是三船和澪商量怎麼讓你感染礦石病的那段，那是我放出來提醒你的！這樣還不足以讓你相信我嗎？", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是你大半夜把我嚇到睡不著覺的？！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#11$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這這這，畢竟那也是我第一次處理御機——不是，金石台的訊號系統，稍微出了一點問題，不是故意的，真的不是故意的！", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#4$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……嗯。不管怎麼說，如果不是你，我可能已經……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我一開始只是聽說金石台是御機首屈一指的大電視台，就來隨便遞份履歷養活自己罷了。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#11$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但在這裡待越久，越覺得他們其實有點不像話，只有你這個當家花旦還蠻可愛的……結果他們竟然連你也不放過！", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤其是那個三船，如果他是個更像樣一點的傢伙，我也不是不知道拿錢辦事的道理。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是這個傢伙……幫這種人做事，還不如讓我跳海自殺呢。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#23$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈哈。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#23$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才我透過三船的監視系統定位到星熊的位置，就稍微幫你們連線了一下。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？這也能連線的嗎？上次直播的時候，電視台的技術總監連事先設定好的連線都搞了很久……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他的能力也不怎麼樣嘛。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總而言之，現在你聽我的指示，等一下我再讓你跟星熊聯絡一次，讓她在外面接應。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們等一下帶著吉星一起走，聽我的，保證那些笨蛋黑道連你們的影子都摸不到。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#10$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，我不能走。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼傻話？不走，就在這裡等三船拿你開刀？", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我走了之後……又能去哪裡呢？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "南院的地盤這麼大，你想去哪裡就去哪裡啊。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去改名換姓，當一個永遠不知道什麼時候會被人追上的逃亡者？我不要。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羽生萌萌香這個名字不是我自己選的，但事到如今才告訴我，要我捨棄這個名字……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我和死了又有什麼區別？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你認真的？我聽你說的這些話，感覺就像是你已經準備赴死了？你不怕死嗎？", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#5$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道，我只知道自己已經沒有別的活法了。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，不愧是我喜歡的明星。你剛剛那段話還蠻酷的，感覺像是電影裡的台詞。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你打算怎麼樣繼續當明星？金兵衛不讓你當怎麼辦？", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……事到如今，誰還擋在我前面，我就要讓那個傢伙知道，就算是我，被逼到牆角……也是會咬人的。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#11$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金兵衛不是捏造了那麼多怪談嗎？我要告訴全御機的人，他們被騙了，被一個叫金兵衛的人渣徹頭徹尾地騙了。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#11$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還蠻有趣的呢。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更紗，你能幫我連線到整個御機的電視嗎？我要向他們所有人告發金兵衛。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一台一台黑過去，那要弄到什麼時候？", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正他們今天也要搞什麼繼位儀式，原本就要向全城直播，我們只要搭個便車就好了。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前聽到有人說你帶著斷刀什麼的，還在你身上嗎？在直播的時候能派上用場的。", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#9$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和吉星被金兵衛抓住之後，他的手下做的第一件事就是從我身上搜出那把斷刀……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便這樣，即便沒了物證，我也要說。一定要說。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#13$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1900_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#10$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我，我去把那個叫吉星的女生也拉過來，再加上電視那邊的青鬼，到時候我們一起討論，看要怎麼好好修理修理三船！", "name": "更紗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1900_1#10$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g13_rooftop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在哪裡？", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底在……哪裡……", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，我怎麼睡著了……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，難道神明大人已經？！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾輩還沒那麼性急。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您？！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內猛地坐正。"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想回頭去看身後的神明，卻又不敢，生怕那裡其實什麼都沒有，一切不過是夢中之夢。"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他身後開口說話的神明對這樣的反應，似乎也頗為滿意。"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明大人……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久……不見。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您終於願意見我了。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年您讓我們家有了錢，不用再過拮据的苦日子，我很感激。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你花了這麼多年尋找吾輩，就是為了道謝？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然想向您道謝，但我也一直想問您一件事。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您當年……究竟為什麼要離我們而去，為什麼我們一家人幸福的生活，最後連一片殘渣也沒有剩下？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為我們做了什麼觸犯您的事？還是說，命運的力量，就連您也無力阻擋，所以才……乾脆對我避而不見？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……和吾輩有什麼關係？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我也覺得，不該是這樣的……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾輩是說，你追著吾輩，難道只是為了一個理由？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你不是為了能再度把幸福抓在手裡，才無論如何都要跟吾輩見一面的嗎？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然已經重複到煩了，但你當時還年幼，現在多半已經忘得一乾二淨了，所以吾輩就耐心地再說一次。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾輩從來不會贈予人什麼東西。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就當吾輩喜歡一件事好了。只要這件事發生，吾輩就有可能出現在人的身邊。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一件……事？是說“幸福”嗎？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾輩既不是因為生你的氣，也不是因為愧對於你，不過是因為幸福離你而去，才不見你罷了。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，吾輩現在終於有了見你的理由。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此時此刻的你，只要選對了路，就能獲得幸福，遠超你想像的莫大的幸福。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明的聲音一如過去，然而森內卻不知道，是不是自己失去了那份獨屬於孩子的純真，這朝思暮想的聲音，竟潛藏了一絲毛骨悚然的感覺。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為聽過太多謊言了嗎？"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，因為自己聽過太多的謊言，就不由自主地將所有美好的承諾都當成了欺騙。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在不一樣。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請……請您說吧。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在正處在一場風暴的中心。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個叫星熊的鬼，一條叫金兵衛的蛇，還有一條可憐的金魚，再加上你這頭只相信自己鼻子的狼，這些人的命運攪成一團。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，還有個可憐的老頭，已經被害死了。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐵齋先生？！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他一死，你一直心心念念的幸福，終於有了一個能被你抓在手中的機會。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的死……我的……幸福？您這是什麼意思？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且……為什麼？鐵齋為什麼會死？誰殺了他？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這很難猜嗎？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你更應該問自己的是，這很重要嗎？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在站在一個無數人夢寐以求的位置上，森內徹。你手頭有一單大生意。選對了路，你就能得到一切。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您讓我……站在金兵衛那一邊？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金兵衛是個騙子。他不可能放過我。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以這才是一單大生意。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金兵衛當然是個騙子，但他需要你。更確切地說，金石會需要你。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金石會和金石集團的剝離已經到了最後一步，如果不是出了天大的變故，沒有人能攔得住。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切看似都在金兵衛的計算之內，但事情到了現在，他很快就會力不從心了。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為一個在鍛冶町和仁田街一路打拼這麼久還能活下來的人，你的器量並不比金兵衛差多少。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內愣住了。"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他設想過無數種與這位神明再會的場景，卻唯獨沒想過會像今天這樣，聽祂平靜地說出如此……"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……恐怖的話。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您讓我……奪取金兵衛的位置？這就是您所說的幸福？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您是否想過，假如我真的奪走了那個位置，卻沒能力駕馭……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你會得到錢。很多很多的錢。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "錢……？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論有沒有能力，你都會得到錢，一筆也許不如金兵衛撈到的多，但對現在的你而言……難以想像的錢。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "錢，不就是幸福嗎？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年幼的你和你的家人，不正是得到了錢嗎？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座御機、這整個國家，不也是得到了錢，才得到了源源不斷的幸福嗎？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而當錢離你而去的時候，幸福又在哪裡呢？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是……您給我的教誨？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是教誨，只不過是最淺顯不過的道理。", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金兵衛懂，議員懂，生活在御機的人幾乎都懂。而你……你年幼的時候，不也懂這件事嗎？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內只覺得渾身發冷，彷彿夕陽正在它自己放射出的金色光芒中慢慢窒息。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那真的是自己年幼時偶遇的神明嗎？"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，這只是一個怪誕的惡夢……不，是有什麼東西正在矇騙自己，好讓自己徹底死了尋找神明的心？"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但，祂的自稱，祂說話的方式，甚至祂常說的那句“和吾輩有什麼關係”……自己從來都沒有忘記過。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但為什麼，為什麼記憶中的祂就連那句冰冷的撇清都像是某種對自己溫暖的鼓勵，現在卻……"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內張開嘴，不停地喘息著，即便如此仍覺得自己無法在這冰冷的惡夢中喘上哪怕一口氣。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，他把手伸進口袋，拿出了那串鑰匙。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "64_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 250.0, "yTo": 230.0, "duration": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "款式老舊的鑰匙上布滿了劃痕，而鑰匙圈上掛著一枚小小的招財貓。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它已經陪伴他許多年。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "64_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.15, "yScaleFrom": 1.15, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "財富就是幸福，是嗎？", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "久違的神明"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是這樣沒錯。也許我下意識裡一直都是這麼相信的。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您是否想過，在一切的一切之前，我其實……只把您當成一個朋友，一個有點孤僻的孩子的，唯一的朋友。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我看來，這個朋友的確給我帶來了幸福，我很感激，但我根本無法報答這份幸福。無論我做什麼，您都無意接受。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，當我有段時間沒去找您，而您消失不見的時候，我想，那一定是因為，我不僅沒有報答您，甚至還冷落了您。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為，我放棄了唯一的朋友，所以最終才會落得這種下場。我罪有應得。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您敢相信嗎？之前三船對我威逼利誘的時候，我差點也做了差不多的事。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個鬼？", "name": "久違的神明"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。她來救我的時候，我的五臟六腑都因為愧疚攪成一團，即便如此卻還是什麼話都說不出口。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您剛剛告訴我，我完全搞錯了，不是您給我帶來了幸福，而是幸福來了，您才來到了我的身旁，對嗎？", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。", "name": "久違的神明"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了。您是神明……您只是神明，對嗎？", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，把神明當朋友，簡直狂妄至極，而妄圖抓到神明的尾巴，更是痴心妄想。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您願意來見我，願意告訴我，我這麼長時間的人生，完完全全地走到了一條錯路上。一條徹頭徹尾的錯路。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個情報販子……怎麼可能會有貨真價實的朋友？", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "47_g15_eveningglow_L1/47_g15_eveningglow_R1/47_g15_eveningglow_L2/47_g15_eveningglow_R2", "solidwidth": "1280/1280/1280/1280", "solidheight": "720/720/720/720", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 60.0, "yFrom": 720.0, "yTo": 360.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內舉起那串鑰匙，把招財貓的鑰匙圈從上面拿下來。"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他仔細看著那個吊飾，彷彿這樣就能和他背後的神明說話。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我還是想要朋友。真正的朋友。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這樣說，您能明白嗎？您……會生氣嗎？", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "久違的神明"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您沒有生氣，我甚至還想……冒昧地……跟您打一個賭。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內把手伸到前方，伸到沒有水泥牆壁阻擋的半空之中。"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我照您說的做……", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一輩子，我永遠也不可能再獲得真正的朋友……", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真正的幸福。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他咬著嘴唇，鬆開顫抖的手。"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個吊飾就像再普通不過的雜物一樣，筆直地向下掉落，很快就被橘黃色夕陽下的黑色街巷吞噬。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g13_rooftop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……再見了。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.4, "bend": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要去哪裡？", "name": "久違的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1903_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去找星熊。如果真的像您說的，連鐵齋都遇害了，那麼我無論如何都得去幫星熊一把。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#5$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hastybell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在仁田街的後巷裡哦，有間小小神社的那一條。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦……咦？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦什麼咦，是我！", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "招財貓大人，祂——", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內下意識地轉頭望去，那裡空空如也，彷彿從一開始就什麼都不曾存在過，除了傍晚橘黃色的空氣。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等他把頭轉回前方的時候，那位好事的神明正飄浮在他眼前的半空中。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你拒絕了祂，祂就走了，很奇怪嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您……又為什麼要幫我？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才不想幫你。是我們神社的人氣王，他說總是吃你的竹輪，很不好意思，讓我有空幫你一下。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是的，想幫忙就自己來幫啊！", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝您來相助，也請幫我多謝那位……呃……“人氣王”？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別以為我會幫你打什麼架，我就是幫你指個路罷了。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到底，我們兩個都被三船那個混蛋狠狠擺了一道啊。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g3_jindaalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_leathershoes_fts", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內老闆？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來幫我，還是來阻止我？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫你。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有餘力來幫我，難道你真的找到神明大人了？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祂很好，比我好很多。但我找到了祂，從此之後祂跟我再無關係。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#3$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香呢？她不在你身邊嗎？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我正要去救她——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "o", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內？是森內嗎？", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "電視？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是森內老闆！萌萌香跟我說了，你做的關東煮全東國不分南北第一好吃。等這件事情結束了，你一定要讓我吃吃看哦！", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問您是？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫我更紗就好了。不過現在不是互相自我介紹的時候了！", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，萌萌香、吉星，離麥克風近一點！現在是開作戰會議的時候了！", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了能讓今天的事情順利成功，我準備給整個御機一個這~麼大的驚喜！", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 4.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}